            "title": "Nhận định chứng khoán 14/5: VN-Index có thể giằng co trong biên độ hẹp - VOV",
            "link": "https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMirwFBVV95cUxQdTY5ZWhWU01GVWRFcW9Qc1RMbEdtallNbTNhWG1iZ3ZpTFRVbHZlTGZfelJQcThWQlJleG9UVHprcXZSRXl6bU1pdnhIdGZCZUR0QnJ6dFlFVXhJcmxmQWdCMkx2emZJWl83Y0lkNUMxcEVWT01ZR2RLTlBmQmRsRElKZ2xfZmdlXzAwS0lKSFlDak54TE1QaUM3YXg1M3FPLTliS1NvVjk4U2VZUG40?oc=5",
